{"tid":599574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足 大家點睇  西亞李畢福 Shia LaBeouf","createTime":"2018-03-20T14:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T04:09:22.000Z","uid":62289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1174183f63860f9ba165940ffaeb03d3414238","tid":599574,"uid":62289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:00:49.000Z","msg":"21歲 已經擔正 Transformers男主角 <br />\n成8億美金票房<br />\n之後Indiana Jones   wall street <br />\nTransformers 2、3 <br />\n直至 11年 加埋 票房加埋都超過40億美金 <br />\n 講緊都係 25歲 <br />\n之後開始唔再拍商業電影 <br />\n仲開始痴痴地線 又抄襲人 <br />\n又笠個牛皮袋上頭去影展 又隊草睇劇 發作 <br />\n<br />\n演技我覺佢幾好 睇fury 表情 動作 <br />\n眼神 都好過brad pitt 前排有個訪問 <br />\n話唔想人地拍緊出色既電影 <br />\n自己仲on99 係到搵咩能量方塊<br />\n幾欣賞佢<br />\n<br />\n仲有樣野 就係佢既著衫style <br />\n係勁有個人風格 連kanye west 都受佢影響<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/215850_2435e90c07170b76e763431580cae98e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F215850_2435e90c07170b76e763431580cae98e.png&h=c3039036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/215854_7e83a6d9d15827d8c0dbc8c03856437f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F215854_7e83a6d9d15827d8c0dbc8c03856437f.png&h=0480ea71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/215905_d6edfcbea2a827a740b929290dbf9ac3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F215905_d6edfcbea2a827a740b929290dbf9ac3.png&h=27123d20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a40b5715edf4b1b01adb4b6e288adf3c3800edc","tid":599574,"uid":62289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/223438_b65ce6a678d07eb201f9a9596d3948a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2